      Product Description

      About us:

      Our company is based in Shenzhen, China.

      The brand is D1D9. In 2008, we began designing and making house alarm systems and smart products.

      D1D9 have a full range in home smart products.

      In 2013, Passed ISO9001.

      In 2015, the company is SHENZHEN CHAMBER OF E- BUSINESS, vice president of the association.

      Today our company have 10 research and develop engineer and 60 other employee.

      Main machine are 1 YAMAHA SMT machine and 4 injection mold machine in factory.

      The alarm system support GSM and wifi

      Main Features

      1. Remote control arm, disarm, monitor and intercom by phone.
      2. 8 wired defense zones and 100 wireless defense zones.
      3. Real-time,delay,24hours,bypass defense zones programming function.
      4. Users can make call by using keypad alarm panel, just like a telephone
      5. LCD display. built-in clock, operate easily
      6. Can store 6 group of phone numbers; when alarming, system will make alarm call to these numbers automatically.
      7. Apply advanced mobile communication technology support SMS and dialing alarm.
      8. Can store 2 group of SMS number; when alarming, system will send alarming SMS automatically.
      9. Built-in AAA NI-HI rechargeable battery that make alarm when power off.
      10. 10-second automatic message recording.

      PIR Motion Detector

      The motion detector is designed for use on interior walls.

      When someone move on front,the alarm system will sound.

      However,the sensors can be set to Out Arm Active mode as per your need.

      Remote Control

      Wireless Key to quickly away-arm,home-arm and disarm your home,and to trigger an emergency alarm.

      Window/Door sensor

      The window/door sensor are installed on the door or window.

      When someone push the door/window over 1 inch(2.54cm),this alarm system will sound.

      Wired siren

      Connect to the main unit.

      Volume:100db.

      • Main unit x1
      • PIRX5
      • Remote controllerx4
      • Door contactx12

      How customer reviews and ratings work

      Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

      To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.
